## Topic: `code-analyzer` / `scanner` — Static analysis

`code-analyzer` is the v5 rewrite; `scanner` is legacy v4. This repo uses PMD via `config/pmd-ruleset.xml` directly — these are available if you need rule discovery beyond PMD.

```bash
sf code-analyzer config
sf code-analyzer rules --rule-selector pmd
sf code-analyzer run --workspace force-app/main/default/classes --output-file report.html

# Legacy
sf scanner rule list --engine pmd
sf scanner rule describe --rulename OperationWithLimitsInLoop
sf scanner run --target force-app/main/default/classes --engine pmd --pmdconfig config/pmd-ruleset.xml
sf scanner run dfa --target force-app --projectdir .
sf scanner rule add --language apex --path ./my-rules
sf scanner rule remove --path ./my-rules
```

